						<div class="postbody">It <strong>could</strong> but it would be difficult. say regular enemies explode with a 32x32 explosion, but when bosses do, they'll explode with a 64x64 explosion. Since large enemies aren't going to be present through out the entire level and only specific areas, it could work then if you change the frames in the explosion by using DMA. (can't DMA change about 8 64x64 sprites in one frame?) So the explotion wouldn't fit in vram, but it could still work in specially scripted areas.</div>

